    public class SortedMapBackedDiscreteFunction<X extends java.lang.Comparable<X>,Y>
extends java.lang.Object
implements DiscreteFunction<X,Y>, java.io.Serializable
    This implementation of KeyValueFunction only provides values at discrete points of X argument. If value is requested for unavailable value an IllegalDiscreteFunctionUsageException is thrown.
